OL,7,FA disqualified driver who caused the
OL,8,Fdeath of a five-year-old boy has had a
OL,9,Fbid to reduce his sentence dismissed
OL,10,Fin the Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FLayton Darwood was five years old when
OL,13,Fhe was killed in what three senior
OL,14,Fjudges called an "extremely traumatic"
OL,15,Fincident in Fenham, Newcastle, in
OL,16,FAugust 2020.
OL,18,FDarren Jacques was jailed for six
OL,19,Fyears for causing death by driving
OL,20,Fwhile disqualified.
