OL,3,CDisqualified driver who killed boy,
OL,4,Cfive, has bid to reduce sentence
OL,5,Cdismissed
OL,7,FBarristers for Jacques, who was 42
OL,8,Fwhen he was sentenced in December last
OL,9,Fyear, argued at a hearing on Tuesday
OL,10,F(13 August) that the sentence was
OL,11,F"manifestly excessive" and should be
OL,12,Freduced.
OL,14,FThe judges, however, threw out the
OL,15,Fappeal bid stating that the sentence
OL,16,Fwas "fully merited" and that the
OL,17,Fchallenge was "not arguable."
