OL,7,FGiving their ruling, Mr Justice
OL,8,FCavanagh, sitting with Lord Justice
OL,9,FWarby and Mr Justice Wall, said: "A
OL,10,Fsentence of six years' imprisonment is
OL,11,Ffully merited.
OL,13,F"It is not unjust in the circumstances
OL,14,Fof the case."
OL,16,FJacques, previously of Penrith,
OL,17,FCumbria, had 26 convictions for 54
OL,18,Foffences between 1997 and 2023,
OL,19,Fincluding 11 motoring offences.
