OL,7,FHe had also been disqualified from
OL,8,Fdriving four times, including once in
OL,9,F2018, with the judges describing his
OL,10,Frecord as "appalling" and as showing
OL,11,F"habitual flouting" of the law.
OL,13,FAlthough Jacques was still banned on
OL,14,Fthe day of the incident in Fenham, he
OL,15,Fhad been driving a Ford Transit tipper
OL,16,Ftruck for work between Durham and
OL,17,FNewcastle.
OL,19,FThe truck had a digger on a trailer
OL,20,Fattached at the back when he stopped
OL,21,Fat a shop to buy alcohol.
